graph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Profet Moses bin kisim ol lo long God, na em bin givim long ol manmeri bilong God, bipo long ol bin go kamap long graun God bin promis long givim ol. Ol bin raitim pinis ol dispela lo na em kamap olsem, as bilong stat bilong sios lo bilong ol manmeri Juda. Na bihain ol sios lida kamapim moa lo ol i tokim long maus tasol, antap long ol lo bin raitim pinis long en. Kamapim lo nating nating na i givim hevi long ol manmeri."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Koban/presen"},{"type":"text","text":" i kam long stat bilong tokples Hibru wod, i tok long \"ol presen bin makim pinis long givim i go long God, o ofa bilong givim God.\" Taim ol manmeri i mekim dispela kain ofa, ol i save mekim tu tok promis long ol dispela samting i makim pinis bilong God, na i no inap long kisim bek long God. Dispela em i no pilai pilai promis. I gat ol bikpela hevi bilong en sapos ol manmeri i brukim dispela tok promis na givim ofa long sampela man."}]}]}}]', [ContentSize] = 12914, Updated = GETUTCDATE() WHERE Id = @TextResourceContentId;

