aimon—em mas i stap klostu long sinagok. Jisas i no stap insait long dispela hap bilong stori, tasol mipela i save olsem em bin go wantaim 4-pela disaipel long haus bilong Saimon na Andru."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mipela i no save wanem kain skin hot sik meri tambu bilong Saimon i kisim o hamas mun o yia em stap wantaim dispela sik. Tasol i tru olsem meri bilong Saimon, em mama bilong en, em i save stap long sik bed long dispela haus wantaim ol. Olsem na Jisas i oraitim em na pinisim stret dispela sik. Wantu tasol em i kirap, nogat moa skin sles na em i hepim ol. Em mas kukim apinun kaikai bilong ol."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Long apinun san i go daun stret, ol manmeri i kisim ol sik man i kam long Jisas. Long dei Sabat taim bilong malolo, ol manmeri i no save mekim wok olsem long karim ol sik man long mat. Em olsem tasol, Sabat i pinis long taim san i go daun, olsem na em orait long ol manmeri i helpim ol sik man i kam long Jisas. Jisas bin givim skul na oraitim man i gat spirit nogut insait long sinagok, ol bin harim pinis nius bilong Jisas, olsem na ol i gat bikpela tingting olsem em bai i oraitim ol tu."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Olgeta hap bilong dispela taun i kam bum long dua bilong dispela haus, na em bikpela lain manmeri tru—o bai yumi tok olsem, olgeta manmeri long taun i kam. Wanwan man i kam wantaim wanwan sik bilong em yet. Tasol ol manmeri i gat sik i kam klia, i no wankain olsem ol man i gat spirit nogut."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Stop long hia na diskas wantaim trensleisen grup bilong yu: Long wei na pasin bilong yupela, ol man i gat sik long bodi i luk narapela kain olsem wanem, long ol man i gat spirit nogut? Tupela i save wok narapela kain olsem wanem, na long wanwan hevi ol man i save hepim ol olsem wanem? Insait long ol dispela tok i stap insait, i kamap klia olsem ol man i gat sik luk narapela kain long ol man i gat spirit nogut."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Taim Jisas i rausim spirit nogut i go aut, em i tokim ol manmeri long noken tokaut long ol arapela man, em i husait. Jisas i no redi long ol manmeri bai save olsem, em Pikinini Man bilong God, tasol dispela spirit nogut em bin rausim i go aut long pastaim, em i kolim nem pinis olsem Jisas em \"Holi Wan bilong God\" Jisas i nid long mekim ol spirit nogut i stap isi inap ol manmeri i noken save, Jisas em husait, na ol bai traim long mekim Jisas bai i wokim ol samting em i no kam long mekim long en."}]}]}},{"stepNumber":3,"tiptap":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"PAINIM AUT OL WANWAN HAP BILONG STORI"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mak 1:29-34"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Harim gut tok i stap insait wanpela taim gen, stat wantaim isi wan long yupela i ken klia long tok ol i tanim na raitim long en."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Insait long dispela hap taim, yu helpim ol grup long luksave long stori. Yu bai helpim grup long painim ol hap bilong stori, lain ap bilong stori i stap olsem wanem na ol man husait i stap insait long stori."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela stori em i gat tupela hap bilong en."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Namba wan hap bilong stori:"},{"type":"text","text":" Jisas i go wantaim Saimon na Andru long haus bilong tupela na em i oraitim meri tambu bilong Saimon."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Namba tu hap bilong stori:"},{"type":"text","text":" Bikpela lain manmeri i kam wantaim sik bilong ol long Jisas bai i oraitim ol"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela em ol man i stap insait long namba wan hap bilong stori:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jisas"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Saimon na Andru"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Meri tambu bilong Saimon"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela em ol man i stap insait long namba tu hap bilong stori:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Olgeta man husait i stap insait long namba wan hap bilong stori"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Planti ol sik man na ol manmeri i gat spirit nogut (husait ol i kam long Jisas bihain long san i go daun.)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"olgeta manmeri long taun (husait i kam long lukim Jisas)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ol spirit nogut (husait Jisas i stopim ol long noken toktok)"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Insait long dispela hap taim, wanpela grup mas i gat stori kadbod, drowin aut, o usim sampela gutpela tingting long pulim tingting bilong ol man inap luksave long stori, na long eksen i stap insait long en."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Soim wanem samting i kamap taim Jisas i wok long oraitim ol man insait long haus, na meri tambu bilong Saimon sanap na stat redim kaikai."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Na narapela samting, soim ol bikpela lain manmeri husait i kam insait long namba tu hap long stori."}]}]}},{"stepNumber":4,"tiptap":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"BIHAINIM TOK I STAP INSAIT NA EKTIM AUT."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mak 1:29-34"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Harim gut tok i stap insait wanpela taim, stat wantaim isi wan long yupela i ken klia long tok ol i tanim na raitim long en."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Insait long dispela hap taim, grup bai ektim aut dispela stori."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela stori em i gat tupela hap bilong en."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela em ol man i stap insait long namba wan hap bilong stori:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jisas"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Saimon na Andru"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Meri tambu bilong Saimon"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela em ol man i stap insait long namba tu hap bilong stori:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Olgeta man i stap insait long namba wan hap bilong stori"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Planti ol sik man na ol manmeri i gat spirit nogut (husait ol i kam long Jisas bihain long san i go daun.)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"olgeta manmeri long taun (husait i kam long lukim Jisas)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ol spirit nogut (husait Jisas i stopim ol long noken toktok)"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tokim ol grup long ektim aut dispela stori tupela taim. Ol i mas ektim aut long tokples ol i wok long trensleitim i go long en. Namba wan taim, tokim grup long ektim aut dispela stori na noken stop. Namba tu taim, grup ektim aut gen dispela stori, stopim ol long wanwan hap insait long stori."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Taim grup i ektim aut dispela stori long namba wan taim, putim iyau long harim gut toktok i kamap namel long ol man, toktok i go olsem wanem, stori lain bilong wanwan hap, na oda bilong stori bihainim wanem samting i kamap pastaim. Lukim na painim aut ol impoten o hatpela hap bilong stori, o hap bilong stori long ektim aut na noken lusim. Helpim grup long tingim gut olgeta wanwan hap bilong stori."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Namba tu taim, grup bai i ektim aut gen dispela stori, stopim ol long sampela hap insait long stori."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jisas i go wantaim Saimon na Andru long haus bilong tupela. Jisas i kisim meri tambu bilong Saimon, husait i sik, holim han bilong em, sanapim em na skin hot i lusim em. Orait meri tambu bilong Saimon redim apininun kaikai bilong ol. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Stopim eksen."},{"type":"text","text":" Askim man husait i ektim meri tambu bilong Saimon na, em i pilim olsem wanem long dispela taim stret. Yupela bai harim ol dispela kain tok olsem, \"pilim amamas,\" \"pulap wantaim ol tok tenkyu,\" o \"pilim orait na redi long helpim,\" Statim gen pilai."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Insait long namba tu hap bilong stori, planti manmeri husait ol sik na spirit nogut i stap insait long en manmeri i kam kamap. Jisas i oraitim planti bilong ol na rausim spirit nogut i go aut. Ol spirit nogut i save husait em Jisas, tasol em i no larim ol long toktok. Bihain grup pinis long ektim aut dispela stori, askim ol, ol i ting olsem wanem long dispela. Askim ol man husait i ektim ol spirit nogut, \"Yupela save husait em Jisas?\" Yupela bai harim ol dispela kain tok olsem, \"Pikinini Man bilong God,\" \"Mesaia,\" \"Man husait i gat olgeta namba,\" o \"God.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Nau askim man husait i ektim Jisas, \"Bilong wanem yu no laikim ol spirit nogut long toktok?\" Yupela bai harim ol dispela kain tok olsem, \"Em i no taim bilong manmeri bai luksave long mi,\" \"Mi no laikim ol spirit nogut i tokaut long mi husait\" o \"Mi bai i stap long kontrol taim mi mekim mi yet kamap ples klia.\""}]}]}},{"stepNumber":5,"tiptap":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"PULAPIM SPEIS"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mak 1:1:29-34"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Harim gut tok i stap insait wanpela taim, stat wantaim isi wan long yupela i ken klia long tok ol i tanim na raitim long en."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"go stret"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bihain long Jisas i kam aut long sinagok, em i go stret long haus bilong Saimon na Andru,. Ating haus bilong Saimon na Andru i klostu long sinagok."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Sinagok"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sinagok em ol lotu ples bilong ol manmeri Juda, inap long ol bai go long bikpela haus lotu long Jerusalem, tasol ol manmeri long hauslain i save kam bum long en haus. Ol manmeri i no save mekim ofa insait long ol sinagok. Dispela em ol hauslain lotu manmeri bilong ol Juda husait i save kam bum long Sabat (lotu dei bilong malolo) na spesol taim bilong bum kaikai, prea, ridim ol tok i stap long buk baibel, na sampela taim long skelim ol hevi bilong komuniti."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"mama bilong meri bilong Saimon"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela meri Jisas i oraitim em, em mama bilong meri bilong Saimon. Long tokples bilong yupela, usim wod yupela i save usim long toktok long meri tambu bilong man, husait i mareti pikinini meri bilong en."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Skin hot sik"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Long ol dispela taim i go pinis, ol manmeri i no bin save, em wanem kain sik. Long kisim skin hot sik i minim ol kainkain sik. Dispela stori i no klia long wanem kain skin hot sik em bin gat, o em bin kisim dispela sik olsem wanem."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Ol tokim Jisas \"long em\" i minim ol i tokim Jisas olsem em i sick."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"long em\""},{"type":"text","text":" dispela tok em i no klia, tasol ol mas bin tokim Jisas olsem, dispela meri i sik— bikos Jisas i go insait long oraitim sik bilong em."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Taim Jisas i "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"helpim em na kirapim em long sanap,"},{"type":"text","text":" Jisas i holim han long sapotim em long sanap, long hap em i slip i stap long en, long kirap na sindaun."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela hap tok, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"em i helpim ol"},{"type":"text","text":" o "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"em bin weit long ol"},{"type":"text","text":" i no tok moa long wanem em i mekim; em olsem tasol, em i redim apinun kaikai bilong ol, long bipo yet long dispela taim, em mas olsem wok bilong em long mekim."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"spirit nogut i stap insait"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Spirit nogut i save makim ol man long go insait long ol, bikos ol i laik long bagarapim ol man na ol gutpela sindaun insait long ol komuniti. Taim ol spirit nogut i go insait long ol man, ol i save kotrolim eksen bilong ol."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Stop long hia na diskas wantaim trensleisen grup: Insait long wei na pasin bilong yupela, ol man spirit nogut i stap insait long en, ol i save mekim wanem?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Ol dimon"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela wod i stap long hia, em inap long senisim wantaim dispela wod "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"nogut/ol doti spirit."}]}]}}]', [ContentSize] = 16190, Updated = GETUTCDATE() WHERE Id = @TextResourceContentId;

