UPDATE ResourceContents SET [DisplayName] = N'Mak 12:35-37', [Version] = 1, [Completed] = 1, [Trusted] = 1, [Content] = N'[{"stepNumber":1,"tiptap":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Harim gut stori i stap insait long buk Mak 12:35-37 na putim i go insait long tingting bilong yupela. Harim gut tok i stap insait tripela taim. (long tripela wei ol i tanim tok long en, sapos em inap) Orait stap olsem wanpela grup na diskasim ol dispela kwesten"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Yupela i laikim wanem hap insait long dispela stori?"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Wanem hap bilong stori yupela i no laikim o i no klia long en?"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela stori i tokim yumi wanem long sait bilong Jisas?"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela stori i tokim yumi wanem long sait bilong ol manmeri?"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela stori em bai i wok olsem wanem long laip bilong yumi long olgeta dei?"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Yupela i save long ol man husait i nidim tru dispela stori long harim?"}]}]}]}]}},{"stepNumber":2,"tiptap":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"STRETIM WANWAN HAP BILONG STORI"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mak 12:35-37"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Harim gut tok i stap insait wanpela taim gen, stat wantaim isi wan long yupela i ken klia long tok ol i tanim na raitim long en."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jisas i go het long skulim ol manmeri insait long banis Tempel. Em i askim tupela hatpela kwesten em i no inap long daunim wanpela narapela i go daun. Em i laik soim olsem, tupela haptok wantaim, em i tru, maski tupela wantaim bai i luk olsem em i no inap kamap tru. Dispela em wei bilong ol tisa bilong Juda oltaim i save usim long givim skul."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ol profet bilong Juda i tok olsem, Mesaia o man bilong kisim bek ol manmeri Juda, em bai i kam long lain bilong Devit husait i gat biknem na em i impoten King. Jisas i askim olsem, \"Bilong wanem ol saveman bilong lo i tok olsem, Mesaia em pikinini tasol, o em i kam long lain bilong King Devit?\" Orait Jisas i tok olsem, Holi Spirit i givim tingting long King Devit long mekim dispela tok i stap insait long Buk Song 110."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Bikpela i tokim Bikpela bilong mi olsem,"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Yu sindaun long hansut bilong mi"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"inap mi putim ol birua bilong yu"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"i stap aninit long lek bilong yu.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Devit yet i kolim dispela man Bikpela bilong en—Mesaia—long sindaun long hansut, o long ples bilong kisim biknem. Long pasin bilong ol Juda, man i sindaun long hansut i gat pawa wantaim King long bosim ol manmeri. God i wok long tokim Mesaia olsem, Mesaia wantaim em yet (God) bai i bosim ol manmeri. God bai i putim ol birua bilong Mesaia i stap aninit long en. Dispela em wanpela piksa bilong man i winim pait, em bai i putim lek antap long ol nek bilong ol birua, em i daunim ol long pait."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Stop long hia na diskas olsem trensleisen grup: God na ol impoten lida i save mekim gut long wanpela man olsem wanem? Long hia, God i putim Mesaia long hansut bilong en, olsem na tupela i ken bosim dispela Kingdom wantaim."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Yupela i save mekim gut long givim biknem na pawa long wanpela man olsem wanem long pasin na wei bilong yupela?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"God i givim pawa long Mesaia na em i winim ol birua bilong en taim em i putim ol i kam long lek bilong en. Long wei na pasin bilong yupela, ol man i winim pait i save mekim wanem long ol birua taim ol i winim pait?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ol King na ol papa, ol i no bin kolim pikinini lain bilong ol olsem, bikpela o masta, em olsem na em hat long Devit bai i kolim wanpela bilong pikinini lain bilong en olsem, bikpela o masta."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Stop long hia na diskas olsem trensleisen grup: Long pasin na wei bilong yupela, ol i save lukim ol pikinini lain bilong ol olsem wanem? Yupela i save lukim ol pikinini lain bilong yupela olsem, ol impoten o ol i gat pawa?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jisas i askim olsem, \"Hau na Mesaia bai i kam long pikinini lain bilong Devit o long pikinini bilong King Devit, long wanem Devit i kolim Mesaia olsem ''bikpela bilong mi''?\" Sampela manmeri i bilip olsem, Mesaia bai i kamapim gen Kingdom bilong Devit long dispela graun. Em olsem tasol, Jisas i traim long soim olsem, wok bilong en long kamapim wanpela bikpela Kingdom bilong God. Jisas i no traim long tok giaman olsem, Mesaia em pikinini lain bilong King Devit. Tasol, Jisas i laik ol manmeri i mas kisim bikpela tingting long Mesaia ol bin tingting i stap long en. Sapos em i tok giaman olsem, Mesaia bai i kam long ol pikinini lain bilong King Devit, ol bikpela lain manmeri bai i belhat long em, long wanem ol bin skulim ol olsem, Mesaia em bai i kam long pikinini lain bilong King Devit. Em olsem tasol, Jisas i soim hau King Devit bin luksave long Mesaia bai i kamap bikpela olsem em i stap."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ol manmeri i amamas tru long harim. Ating ol i laikim olsem, ol saveman bilong lo, ol i pilim amamas long ol skul tok bilong Jisas. Ol toktok we ol manmeri i bekim i soim olsem, Jisas em bikpela save pes long ol bikpela lain manmeri."}]}]}},{"stepNumber":3,"tiptap":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"PAINIM AUT OL WANWAN HAP BILONG STORI"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mak12:35-37"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Harim gut tok i stap insait wanpela taim gen, stat wantaim isi wan long yupela i ken klia long tok ol i tanim na raitim long en."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Insait long dispela hap taim, yu bai helpim grup long luksave long stori. Yu bai helpim grup long painim ol hap bilong stori, lain ap bilong stori i stap olsem wanem, na ol man husait i stap insait long stori."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela stori em i gat wanpela hap bilong en."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Insait long namba wanpela hap bilong stori:"},{"type":"text","text":" Jisas i skulim ol manmeri insait long banis Tempel. Em i askim wanpela kwesten long helpim ol long tingim gut, wanem wok tru bilong Mesaia o man bilong kisism bek ol manmeri."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela em ol man i stap insait long stori:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jisas"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ol disaipel (ol i no mekim wanpela samting insait long dispela hap bilong stori, tasol ating ol i stap wantaim Jisas long banis Tempel.)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ol manmeri i stap insait long banis Tempel, wantaim ol saveman bilong lo"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Kind Devit (Jisas i tok olsem King Devit bin tokim insait long Holi Buk bilong God longpela taim i go pinis)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"BIKPELA God"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bikpela Masta o Mesaia"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Insait long dispela hap taim, grup mas i gat stori kadbod, drowin aut, o usim sampela gutpela tingting long pulim tingting bilong ol man inap luksave long stori, na long eksen i stap insait long en."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Em impoten long tingim gut olsem, Jisas i stap yet insait long banis Tempel. Ating em i mas skulim ol bikpela lain manmeri insait long banis, na ol disaipel bilong en i stap yet wantaim em."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Em impoten long tingim gut olsem, Jisas bin skulim ol manmeri olsem, planti saveman bilong lo i save skulim. Em i askim planti kwesten insait long tok em i skulim ol."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Em impoten long tingim gut olsem, Jisas i autim tok i stap insait long Buk Song."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Stop long hia na tingim, sapos yupela i usim narapela kain nek, o tok taim ol i tokaut long tok i stap long Holi Buk bilong God."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jisas i autim tok long ol manmeri wanem Devit i bin toktok long Mesaia na raitim insait long Buk Song. Jisas i tok olsem, Holi Spirit bin tokim Devit long tok olsem, \"Bikpela (God) i tokim Bikpela bilong mi (o masta bilong mi): Yu sindaun long hansut bilong mi, inap mi putim ol birua bilong yu"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"i stap aninit long lek bilong yu.\" Devit i tok olsem, God i tok long masta bilong en o long masta bilong Devit bai i sindaun long hansut long ples bilong kisim biknem. God bai i givim em strong long winim ol birua bilong en. Em bai i soim dispela, taim em i putim ol birua aninit long lek bilong masta bilong Devit."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Em impoten long tingim gut olsem, ol bikpela lain manmeri ol i amamas long harim dispela skul tok Jisas i autim."}]}]}},{"stepNumber":4,"tiptap":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"BIHAINIM TOK I STAP INSAIT NA EKTIM AUT"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mak 12:35-37"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Harim gut tok i stap insait wanpela taim gen, stat wantaim isi wan long yupela i ken klia long tok ol i tanim na raitim long en."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Long dispela hap taim, grup bai i kamapim pilai bilong dispela stori"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela stori em i gat wanpela pela hap bilong en."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispela em ol man i stap insait long stori:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jisas"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ol disaipel (ol i no mekim wanpela samting insait long dispela hap bilong stori, tasol ating ol i stap wantaim Jisas long banis Tempel.)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ol manmeri i stap insait long banis Tempel, wantaim ol saveman bilong lo"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Kind Devit (Jisas i tok olsem King Devit bin tokim insait long Holi Buk bilong God longpela taim i go pinis"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bikpela God"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bikpela Masta o Mesaia"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tokim grup long ektim aut dispela stori tupela taim. Namba wan taim, tokim grup ektim aut dispela stori na no ken stop. Namba tu taim, grup ektim aut dispela stori na stopim ol long wanwan hap insait long stori."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Taim grup i ektim dispela stori namba wan taim, putim iyau long harim gut toktok i kamap namel long ol man, toktok i go olsem wanem, stori lain bilong wanwan hap, na oda bilong stori bihainim wanem samting i kamap pastaim."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Grup i mas ektim aut Jisas bin skulim ol manmeri insait long banis bilong Tempel. Ating em bin stap long hap sampela taim liklik, taim em i skulim ol manmeri. Ol disaipel bilong en tu bin stap long hap. Jisas i statim dispela hap stori wantaim wanpela kwesten em i askim, \"Bilong wanem ol saveman bilong lo i tok olsem, Mesaia em pikinini bilong Devit?\" Orait Jisas i go het na tok olsem, \"Holi Spirit i givim tingting long Devit na em i tok olsem, ''God (o Bikpela) i tok long bikpela bilong mi (o masta bilong mi), sindaun long sia bilong kisim biknem long hansut inap mi putim ol birua bilong yu i stap aninit long lek bilong yu. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Stopim pilai"},{"type":"text","text":". Askim ol manmeri, \"Yuppela i pilim olsem wanem?\" Yupela bai i harim dispela kain tok olsem, \"Mipela i kirap nogut,\" \"tingting i paul,\" \"tingting planti.\" Statim gen pilai."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Grup i mas ektim aut Jisas bin mekim wanpela tok bilong pinisim skul toktok bilong en, em i tok olsem, \"Devit em yet i kolim Mesaia ''Bikpela bilong mi,'' hau na Mesaia bai kamap pikinini lain bilong em?\" "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Stopim pilai"},{"type":"text","text":". Askim ol manmeri, \"Yupela i pilim olsem wanem?\" Yupela bai i harim dispela kain tok olsem, \"Mipela i amamas, long wanem Jisas i gat nupela tok bilong skulim na gutpela skul tok,\" \"Tingting i paul liklik,\" o \"Mipela i amamas long wanem, Jisas i toktok wantaim pawa.\""}]}]}},{"stepNumber":5,"tiptap":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"PULAPIM SPEIS"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mak 12:35-37"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Harim gut tok i stap insait wanpela taim, stat wantaim isi wan long yupela i ken klia long tok ol i tanim na raitim long en."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jisas i skulim ol manmeri insait long banis "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tempel"},{"type":"text","text":". Tingting gut long usim sem wod long Tempel olsem yupela bin usim i kam long ol pastaim stori, tingim gut olsem Tempel i stap long bikpela wod list."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jisas i askim, bilong wanem ol "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"saveman bilong lo"},{"type":"text","text":" o ol "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"skraip"},{"type":"text","text":" i tok olsem, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Mesaia"},{"type":"text","text":" o "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Krais"},{"type":"text","text":", em bilong "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"pikinini bilong lain"},{"type":"text","text":" bilong Devit o pikinini bilong "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Devit"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Usim sem wod long saveman bilong lo, Mesaia o Krais, olsem yupela bin usim i kam long buk Mak, na tingim gut olsem, ol dispela wod i stap long bikpela wod list."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Pikinini bilong Devit"},{"type":"text","text":", em i minim pikinini bilong lain bilong Devit. Insait long Nupela Testament, dispela wod, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"pikinini bilong Devit"},{"type":"text","text":", em i tok long Mesaia, bikos ol profet bin tok pinis olsem Mesaia bai i kam long lain bilong King Devit."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"King Devit"},{"type":"text","text":" em bikpela man na impoten king bilong ol manmeri Juda. God bin tok promis pinis long Devit olsem, wanpela man long lain bilong em bai i bosim ol Israel oltaim oltaim. King Devit i stap long bikpela wod list."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Jisas i tok olsem, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Holi Spirit"},{"type":"text","text":" i givim tingting long Devit long em bai i tok wanem taim em i raitim Buk Song bilong en. Insait long Olpela Testamen long tokples Hibru, ruak [spirit] em i ken minim dispela ''win i save ron long speis o win man i save pulim.'' Em i minim tu ''pawa'' o ''namba'' God i givim long wanpela man long mekim ol bikpela samting. Olpela Testamen piksa tok bilong dispela tingting i tok long Spirit bilong God, em i stap insait long dispela stori bilong kapsaitim wel antap long Devit. Insait long dispela stori kwiktaim Spirit bilong God i kam insait long Devit. God bin givim Spirit bilong en long ol king, taim em he kapsaitim oil antap long ol long kamap king, na givim ol spesol save na pawa i kam long God. Dispela man husait i inapim tru wantaim Spirit bilong God i save kisim tok long God na i go long ol manmeri, o long wanwan man. Dispela man husait i gat Spirit bilong God, em i gat gutpela save na pawa i kam long God (em ol king na ol profet). Usim sem wod long "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Holi Spirit"},{"type":"text","text":" olsem yupela bin usim long ol pastaim stori, na tingim gut olsem dispela wod i stap long bikpela wod list."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Taim Devit i tok olsem, \""},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Bikpela"},{"type":"text","text":" i tok long "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Bikpela"},{"type":"text","text":" bilong mi,\" em i tok long taim God i toktok long Mesaia. Dispela namba wan wod, BIKPELA i tok long God. Na namba tu wod, Bikpela i tok long masta bilong Devit (husait yumi save olsem, em Mesaia). Ating yupela nid long mekim klia insait long wok bilong trensleisen bilong yupela olsem, em \"God Bikpela\" husait i tok long \"Bikpela bilong mi "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"text":"masta"},{"type":"text","text":".\""}]}]}}]', [ContentSize] = 18398, Updated = GETUTCDATE() WHERE Id = @TextResourceContentId;

